query:
UPDATE island_guides ig
JOIN places p ON LOWER(REPLACE(ig.name, ' ', '')) = LOWER(REPLACE(p.name, ' ', ''))
SET ig.placeId = p.id
WHERE ig.placeId IS NULL AND p.type = 'island'
